data.name: label22.Text
data.value: Ametus Development Co., Ltd. was founded by Mr. Chairit Chaisitthiroj and Acting Sub Lt. Varot Jintananuwat, a real estate development business specializing in pool villas, single homes and condominiums, currently with the registered capital of 100 million baht. Both businessmen are veterans in real estate development, specializing in condominiums, with a professional team and experts in real estate development projects come together to develop ideas and directions to operate effectively to provide utmost satisfaction for our customers.
